definitions.definition: A maritime traditional county of Wales , bounded to the north by Caernarfonshire , to the east by Denbighshire , to the south by Montgomeryshire and Cardiganshire , and to the west by Cardigan Bay .

main_definition: A maritime traditional county of Wales , bounded to the north by Caernarfonshire , to the east by Denbighshire , to the south by Montgomeryshire and Cardiganshire , and to the west by Cardigan Bay .
